A few weeks back it was annonced that bard would get a new line of Songs that WOULD stack with Enchanter Haste lines... So yes he is right, haste items are about to go down in price, not by much but they will. And I see a new influx of Bard tweeks as well for Uber Guilds...<br>
<br>
The was these songs were presented was that it would would actually push the haste cap up, over what it is now. So Haste items will still be in demaned but not overly so I guess...<br>
<br>
Shissar+Haste item+Bard Song = New Haste Cap.<br>
